project_descr: Sustainable System of Navigational Aids for Approach Channel  Umm Qasr & Az Zubayr Ports

outputs.output_title: NavAids for Umm Qasr & Az Zuba
outputs.output_descr:
1. Access to Umm Qasr Port improved through provision of effective visual NavAid system.
2. Sustainability of assets supported through staff training & provision of facilities for repair.
3. Institutional & management capacity developed for effective management of port access issues.
4. Provision of technical advice on Automatic Information System/Vessel Tracking System (AIS/VTS).
